{"title":"Aesthetic Retro Photo Prints","description":"\u003ch2\u003e📄 Product Description\u003c\/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eTurn your favorite memories into timeless keepsakes with our \u003cstrong\u003eCustom Retro Photo Prints\u003c\/strong\u003e — beautifully printed on premium glossy paper with a clean white border and optional personalized captions. Whether you're decorating your space, gifting moments to loved ones, or cherishing travel highlights, these prints add the perfect personal touch.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch3\u003e✨ Why You’ll Love It\u003c\/h3\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e📸 \u003cstrong\u003eUpload \u0026amp; Personalize\u003c\/strong\u003e – Just upload your photos and we’ll handle the printing with care\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e✏️ \u003cstrong\u003eOptional Captions\u003c\/strong\u003e – Add a meaningful message or quote under each photo\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e📏 \u003cstrong\u003eChoose Your Size\u003c\/strong\u003e – Available in \u003cstrong\u003e3.5 x 4.2”\u003c\/strong\u003e (classic) or \u003cstrong\u003eA6\u003c\/strong\u003e (larger and bolder)\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e💎 \u003cstrong\u003ePremium Print Quality\u003c\/strong\u003e – Sharp, vibrant prints on glossy photo paper\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e🎁 \u003cstrong\u003eGreat for Gifting, Scrapbooks \u0026amp; Decor\u003c\/strong\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e🇮🇳 \u003cstrong\u003eMade in India • Delivered Across India\u003c\/strong\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003ch3\u003e📦 What’s Included\u003c\/h3\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eA set of \u003cstrong\u003e10 \/ 20 \/ 30 \/ 40 \/ 50\u003c\/strong\u003e Retro Photo Prints\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eWith or without custom captions (as per your selection)\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eAvailable in two sizes:\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e🟢 \u003cstrong\u003e3.5 x 4.2 inch\u003c\/strong\u003e – Compact and aesthetic\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e🟢 \u003cstrong\u003eA6 size\u003c\/strong\u003e – Larger with more visual impact\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003ch3\u003e🧠 How It Works\u003c\/h3\u003e\n\u003col\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eChoose your \u003cstrong\u003eQuantity\u003c\/strong\u003e (10 to 50 prints)\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eSelect whether you want \u003cstrong\u003eCaptions\u003c\/strong\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ePick your \u003cstrong\u003eSize\u003c\/strong\u003e (3.5 x 4.2” or A6)\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eUpload your photos\u003c\/strong\u003e – from your device, Google Drive, or social media\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cem\u003e(Optional)\u003c\/em\u003e Add notes or captions per photo or a single title for the set\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003ePlace your order\u003c\/strong\u003e – we’ll print, pack, and deliver with care\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ol\u003e\n\u003ch3\u003e🔄 Important Notes\u003c\/h3\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eIf fewer photos are uploaded than selected, we’ll fill remaining prints with \u003cstrong\u003eaesthetic quote designs\u003c\/strong\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eEvery print includes a \u003cstrong\u003eclassic white Retro Photo Printsborder\u003c\/strong\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFor bulk orders (above 100 prints), email us for a custom deal\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003ch3\u003e🚚 Shipping Info\u003c\/h3\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e📦 Dispatched in \u003cstrong\u003e2–3 working days\u003c\/strong\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e🛵 Delivered anywhere in India (\u003cstrong\u003eCOD \u0026amp; Prepaid available\u003c\/strong\u003e)\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e🔍 Track your order anytime via your Posterized account\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003ch3\u003e💬 Need Help?\u003c\/h3\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eEmail us at \u003ca href=\"mailto:support@posterized.in\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003esupport@posterized.in\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/a\u003e — our team is always happy to help.\u003c\/p\u003e","products":[{"product_id":"custom-retro-prints","title":"Custom Retro Prints","description":"\u003cp\u003ePremium high-definition wall poster of \u003cstrong\u003eCustom Retro Prints\u003c\/strong\u003e, designed to instantly upgrade the aesthetic of your room.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003ePrinted on ultra-thick 300 GSM matte photo paper for rich colours, sharp detailing and a soft anti-glare finish. Long-lasting, fade-resistant and crafted to give your wall a clean, premium look with zero effort.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThis poster blends perfectly into bedroom, living room, gaming setup or workspace décor. Easy to frame, perfect for collage walls, and ideal for anyone who loves aesthetic room vibes, minimal design and high-quality prints.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eA great pick for personal use or gifting — made to match your vibe and elevate your space.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Posterized","offers":[{"title":"3.5 X 4.2\" \/ 10","offer_id":50193718018344,"sku":null,"price":179.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"3.5 X 4.2\" \/ 20","offer_id":50183670169896,"sku":null,"price":319.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"3.5 X 4.2\" \/ 30","offer_id":50183670300968,"sku":null,"price":429.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"3.5 X 4.2\" \/ 40","offer_id":50183670235432,"sku":null,"price":529.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"3.5 X 4.2\" \/ 50","offer_id":50183670366504,"sku":null,"price":629.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"A6 \/ 10","offer_id":50193718083880,"sku":null,"price":199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"A6 \/ 20","offer_id":50184197669160,"sku":null,"price":379.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"A6 \/ 30","offer_id":50184197800232,"sku":null,"price":529.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"A6 \/ 40","offer_id":50184197734696,"sku":null,"price":659.0,"currency_code":"INR"